   <blockquote>
    <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1" width="50%"/>
    <span style="font-weight: 400">
     <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
      OFTEN:
     </p>
     <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
      <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" name="I1" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4dtwTr_w12I?rel=0" width="560">
      </iframe>
      <br/>
     </p>
     The tips of the bent right "b" hand touch the palm of the left hand
  (near the heel of the palm) then separate and move forward a couple inches,
  then make contact again.  If you do this sign quickly, and add another
  movement it would mean "frequently."
     <br/>
     <p>
      <img border="0" height="234" src="/images/often-d1.jpg" width="218"/>
