      <br/>
     </p>
     <p>
      LIBRARY, YOU GO HOW OFTEN?
      <br/>
      <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" name="I2" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ggO7m9orzkg?rel=0" width="560">
      </iframe>
      <br/>
     </p>
     <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
     <p>
      <br/>
      FREQUENTLY:
      <br/>
      The sign for "frequently" can be done the same as the sign for "often." 
	However, some people also add an extra movement and contact. Remember, the contacts move from the palm of the hand (somewhat near the
  heel) toward the fingertips of the hand.
